{"fileHash":"sha256:f0fc3d1cc79ff6397da8ca534fee8037b0722a526d7a22ceb519efad30fccd1b","sections":{"h2-before-you-start":{"contentHash":"sha256:0f0c62a38bb8c4ac8e04a7990e8756d7e746533b356d2156c92a3f80c8cdc65a","proseHash":"sha256:0f0c62a38bb8c4ac8e04a7990e8756d7e746533b356d2156c92a3f80c8cdc65a","translation":"## 开始之前 \\{#before-you-start\\}\n"},"h3-manage-users":{"contentHash":"sha256:1bea73e33413bd12f0e223016524dc7b3442bf8d2ca15879cfeb7c9c6eba584a","proseHash":"sha256:1bea73e33413bd12f0e223016524dc7b3442bf8d2ca15879cfeb7c9c6eba584a","translation":"### 管理用户 \\{#manage-users\\}\n\n您可以选择在后端使用身份验证，也可以不使用。\n\n但是，Adapty SDK 对匿名用户和已识别用户的处理方式不同。请阅读[用户身份识别快速入门指南](capacitor-quickstart-identify)，以了解具体细节并确保您正确处理用户信息。\n"}}}